{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "A minimum of 2 years as PM before the Public Duty Cost Allowance is available.",
        "additional_details": "It will cost the tax payer millions of pounds to honour this unearned, undeserved \u201cperk\u201d of the job. Failure should not be rewarded as it undermines our faith in our parliamentary system",
        "background": "It is unfair that someone serving a few weeks as PM is entitled to an annual allowance of \u00a3115,000. There should be a minimum time spent serving in that capacity before the payments are triggered",
